{"tid":697731,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一個終極女權撚應該付合咩條件？","createTime":"2018-06-11T06:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T11:57:26.000Z","uid":30895,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28ffe5b1d8af639302d968c0b4e25c6040d2bfea","tid":697731,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"首先注意返，係討論女權，唔係討論TB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁究竟如果女權撚要擺脫對女性嘅定形應該要有咩特質先可以令所有人都認同女權係可取？我諗左幾點，不過小弟才疏學淺，需要大家幫手諗下<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人係巴打，都好憎啲偽女權撚，乜柒婦女團體，但係現今社會的確有啲野係默認男女有別，所以先有咁樣嘅諗法<br />\n<br />\n-接受短頭髮/男人長頭髮<br />\n-不能應為女性應該剃體毛<br />\n-不反抗男人著裙<br />\n-支持唔戴BRA，解放乳頭<br />\n-拍拖要求AA制，一切追求平等<br />\n-可以定下重大決定（小至家庭事務，大至公司決策）<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲咩特質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4484df39f0f34d70a2063ac5460ffe321b4f343","tid":697731,"uid":71711,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"AA制有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f1a330d75bda08b85067289787a989b28cd2bd","tid":697731,"uid":113830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"支持男性體內懷孕 炸左自己個子宮"},{"pid":"1ada6bf11cefcbe77439ccdd436ef894ee1d23d5","tid":697731,"uid":44391,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"148b982f6f2a8537fd3777ee48de7ba59db07d7d","tid":697731,"uid":8519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f1a330d75bda08b85067289787a989b28cd2bd","tid":697731,"uid":113830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"支持男性體內懷孕 炸左自己個子宮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4903724e339571840bb157325cfdd9362850